{
  "stem": "24470.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And Moshe had his mother and sister and brother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were very close.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I did not feel that I have the right to separate them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "His mother would not go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I didn't-- he-- if I would ask him, he maybe would agree, because he was very much for living in Israel, too.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I didn't have the heart even to say.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Knowing how the family was close and loving, I decided that I'll go.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I was happy coming to my husband, whom I loved very much and still do, and I was unhappy leaving Israel.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "As a result, as you'll see later, our older daughter took over, was always interested in Israel, was interested in Holocaust, and made aliyah to Israel after going there every summer.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Decided to stay there, remain for life there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Two girls.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One is Maya, and one is Avia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Children here?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Avi and Paul.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they have four children.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Beginning with 12-year-old, every three years down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yossi is the first one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Boaz is the second one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Uh, Isaac is the third one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And Elyiana-- Eli Anna, which is 'God answered'-- is the fourth one.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Three years ago.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm beginning my fourth year.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In October was three years.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we worked in New York all our lives.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was teaching, Moshe was working.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when we retired, it was a question-- one year we remained as retirees in New York.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then we had to travel to Israel to be with our daughter there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had to travel to Pittsburgh to stay with our children here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We decided one place or the other must be our home, because it doesn't make sense for us to travel.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we chose Pittsburgh.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I work in a private Jewish nursery school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I call it-- not really teaching.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
